<ol>
  <li>Place the raspberries, the cinnamon stick and the lemon in a saucepan. Bring to the boil and mash the mixture. Boil for another 1-2 minutes, while constantly stirring.</li>
  <li>Add the sugar and boil the mixture for another 5 minutes.</li>
  <li>Pour into the jars and let it cool overnight.</li>
  <li>Best served on scones.</li>
</ol>
